      <title>BancTrust 称美联储降息或将刺激尼日利亚和安哥拉欧洲债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/fed-cut-may-spur-nigeria-angola-eurobond-sales-banctrust-says</link>
