    <item>
      <title>报告称国泰航空发动机起火可能造成重大损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/cathay-engine-fire-could-have-led-to-major-damage-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[初步报告称，本月早些时候，国泰航空有限公司一架航班的发动机在空中起火，起火原因可能蔓延至飞机并造成大面积损坏，对事故原因和故障部件的调查仍在继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/cathay-engine-fire-could-have-led-to-major-damage-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
