      <title>美联储降息推动亚洲货币创 14 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/asian-currencies-hit-14-month-high-as-fed-slashes-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦储备委员会启动政策放松并暗示今年将进一步降息后，亚洲货币升至一年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/asian-currencies-hit-14-month-high-as-fed-slashes-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:54:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储利率调整有望推动亚洲资产大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/fed-s-rate-pivot-seen-driving-outsized-gain-in-asian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储转向降息对亚洲资产来说是个好兆头，因为许多亚洲资产的持有量不足，而且与全球其他资产相比，它们拥有更好的盈利前景和更大的从宽松政策中获益的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/fed-s-rate-pivot-seen-driving-outsized-gain-in-asian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
