    <item>
      <title>铜价因鲍威尔降息半个百分点创两个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/metals-mixed-after-initial-boost-from-fed-s-half-point-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储降息半个百分点，以捍卫美国经济增长和劳动力市场，金属价格随之上涨，铜价也攀升至 7 月中旬以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/metals-mixed-after-initial-boost-from-fed-s-half-point-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 03:14:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员消化美联储降息影响，比特币随美国股票期货上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/bitcoin-btc-climbs-with-us-equity-futures-as-traders-digest-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储大幅降息对市场产生连锁反应，比特币随美国股指期货上涨触及三周新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/bitcoin-btc-climbs-with-us-equity-futures-as-traders-digest-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 01:22:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员追踪风险偏好基调和中东紧张局势，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储大幅降息后，风险偏好情绪席卷了整个金融市场，同时交易员关注中东地区紧张局势的升级，油价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:40:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元走弱，投资者等待日本央行政策，日本股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japan-s-stock-futures-rise-as-yen-pares-gain-traders-await-boj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔警告不要认为美联储将继续大幅降息，日本股市上涨，日元走弱。投资者正在等待日本央行周五的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japan-s-stock-futures-rise-as-yen-pares-gain-traders-await-boj</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 22:43:12 GMT</pubDate>
